		<descriptionSet>
			<description source=" " lang="en" script="latn">A page from the film brochure of the Hindi movie "Mahaan" shows important scenes from the film. This movie was released in the year 1983 and had the male protagonist, Amitabh Bachhan in a triple role. The poster shows Amitabh in his three roles. In one image, the older character he plays is in a cage with his wife surrounded by flames. His wife Waheeda Rehman cries while Amitabh looks towards the flames. To the bottom left, Amitabh fights the villain, Amjad Khan, who holds a revolver in his hand. To the bottom right of the image, Amitabh figths with the second villain, Shakti Kapoor. To the top left are the female protagonists, Parveen Babi (left) and Zeenat Aman (right).</description>
